{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"2e3f4a5b6c7d8e9f","type":"group","x":-50,"y":650,"width":2800,"height":400,"color":"4","label":"☸️ Kubernetes 集群环境"},
		{"id":"1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-50,"width":1100,"height":600,"color":"6","label":"📦 微服务代码仓库 (20个)"},
		{"id":"2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1100,"width":1400,"height":350,"color":"5","label":"📊 可观测性体系"},
		{"id":"6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a","type":"group","x":1400,"y":1100,"width":1350,"height":350,"color":"1","label":"🔐 安全与治理"},
		{"id":"1d2e3f4a5b6c7d8e","type":"group","x":1700,"y":-50,"width":550,"height":600,"color":"4","label":"📁 GitOps 配置仓库 (env-config)"},
		{"id":"4c5d6e7f8a9b0c1d","type":"group","x":1150,"y":-50,"width":500,"height":600,"color":"2","label":"⚙️ GitLab CI Pipeline"},
		{"id":"6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e","type":"group","x":2300,"y":-50,"width":500,"height":300,"color":"5","label":"🔄 ArgoCD"},
		{"id":"9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6e","type":"group","x":2300,"y":280,"width":500,"height":270,"color":"1","label":"🚢 Kargo (渐进式交付)"},
		{"id":"9e0f1a2b3c4d5e6f","type":"group","x":1800,"y":700,"width":900,"height":300,"color":"1","label":"🔴 PROD 环境 (ns-prod)"},
		{"id":"3e4f5a6b7c8d9e0f","type":"group","x":0,"y":700,"width":850,"height":300,"color":"4","label":"🟢 DEV 环境 (ns-dev)"},
		{"id":"6e7f8a9b0c1d2e3f","type":"group","x":900,"y":700,"width":850,"height":300,"color":"3","label":"🟡 TEST/STAGING 环境 (ns-test)"},
		{"id":"0f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a","type":"text","text":"### 特点\n\n- **严格审批**: Tech Lead + 运维\n- 副本数: 3+ (HPA)\n- 资源限制: 生产级\n- 用途: 生产服务\n\n### 发布节奏\n\n- 周五晚 (常规)\n- 随时 (紧急 hotfix)","x":1850,"y":750,"width":380,"height":200},
		{"id":"1f2a3b4c5d6e7f8a","type":"text","text":"### 回滚策略\n\n修改 prod overlay 镜像 tag\n\n→ 回退到上一版本\n\n→ MR 合并即回滚\n\n**Kargo**: 一键 Rollback","x":2280,"y":750,"width":380,"height":200},
		{"id":"4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f","type":"text","text":"### 特点\n\n- **自动部署**: merge 到 main 即发布\n- 副本数: 1\n- 资源限制: 低\n- 用途: 开发自测 / 联调\n\n### 发布节奏\n\n每次 commit 自动触发","x":50,"y":750,"width":350,"height":200},
		{"id":"5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f","type":"text","text":"### 20个服务 Pod\n\n```\nsvc-user-xxx\nsvc-auth-xxx\nsvc-order-xxx\nsvc-payment-xxx\n...\n(共20个 Deployment)\n```","x":450,"y":750,"width":350,"height":200},
		{"id":"7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f","type":"text","text":"### 特点\n\n- **MR 审批**: 需要 1 人 review\n- 副本数: 2\n- 资源限制: 中\n- 用途: 测试 / 回归 / 验收\n\n### 发布节奏\n\n- 周二晚\n- 周四晚","x":950,"y":750,"width":350,"height":200},
		{"id":"8e9f0a1b2c3d4e5f","type":"text","text":"### 版本管理\n\n语义化版本: `v1.2.3`\n\n从 main 打 tag → CI 构建\n\n创建 MR 修改 test overlay\n\n→ Kargo Promotion","x":1350,"y":750,"width":350,"height":200},
		{"id":"0a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b","type":"text","text":"# 🚀 CI/CD 流水线全景架构图\n\n**20微服务 × GitLab CI × GitOps × ArgoCD × Kargo**\n\n> 代码、镜像、配置、环境全部在 Git 中可追踪，所有环境的变更都通过 Merge Request 审批","x":0,"y":-200,"width":1800,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4a5b6c7d8e9f0a1b","type":"text","text":"**svc-order**\n订单服务","x":440,"y":0,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"5a6b7c8d9e0f1a2b","type":"text","text":"**svc-payment**\n支付服务","x":660,"y":0,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b","type":"text","text":"**svc-product**\n产品服务","x":880,"y":0,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"8a9b0c1d2e3f4a5b","type":"text","text":"**svc-cart**\n购物车服务","x":220,"y":80,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"9a0b1c2d3e4f5a6b","type":"text","text":"**svc-notification**\n通知服务","x":440,"y":80,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"0b1c2d3e4f5a6b7c","type":"text","text":"**svc-search**\n搜索服务","x":660,"y":80,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c","type":"text","text":"**svc-recommend**\n推荐服务","x":880,"y":80,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"3b4c5d6e7f8a9b0c","type":"text","text":"**svc-report**\n报表服务","x":220,"y":160,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c","type":"text","text":"**svc-gateway**\nAPI网关","x":440,"y":160,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"5b6c7d8e9f0a1b2c","type":"text","text":"**svc-config**\n配置中心","x":660,"y":160,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"2d3e4f5a6b7c8d9e","type":"text","text":"### base/ (通用模板)\n\n```\nbase/\n  svc-user/\n  svc-auth/\n  svc-order/\n  ... (20个服务)\n```\n\nDeployment / Service / ConfigMap 模板","x":1750,"y":0,"width":450,"height":150,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e","type":"text","text":"### overlays/dev/\n\n开发环境覆盖配置\n\n- 镜像 tag: `${CI_COMMIT_SHA}`\n- 副本数: 1\n- 资源限制: 较低","x":1750,"y":170,"width":450,"height":130,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e","type":"text","text":"### overlays/test/\n\n测试/预发环境覆盖配置\n\n- 镜像 tag: `v1.2.3` (语义化版本)\n- 副本数: 2\n- 需要 MR 审批","x":1750,"y":320,"width":450,"height":130,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"7d8e9f0a1b2c3d4e","type":"text","text":"### Application CRD\n\n每个环境一个 Application:\n\n- `app-dev` → overlays/dev\n- `app-test` → overlays/test\n- `app-prod` → overlays/prod","x":2350,"y":0,"width":400,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8d9e0f1a2b3c4d5e","type":"text","text":"### 同步策略\n\n- **Dev**: 自动同步 (automated: true)\n- **Test**: 手动同步 + Diff 预览\n- **Prod**: 手动同步 + 审批 + Diff 预览","x":2350,"y":120,"width":400,"height":100,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"0e1f2a3b4c5d6e7f","type":"text","text":"### Stage 定义\n\n`dev` → `test` → `prod`\n\n每个 Stage 对应 K8s 命名空间","x":2350,"y":330,"width":400,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f","type":"text","text":"### Freight 管理\n\n- 自动发现新镜像版本\n- 创建 Freight (版本包)\n- 通过 Promotion 逐级推进","x":2350,"y":430,"width":400,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b","type":"text","text":"**svc-auth**\n认证服务","x":220,"y":0,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d","type":"text","text":"### Stage 1: Lint\n\n代码格式检查、静态分析\n\n`golangci-lint` / `pylint` / `eslint`","x":1200,"y":0,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"6c7d8e9f0a1b2c3d","type":"text","text":"### Stage 2: Test\n\n单元测试 + 覆盖率检查\n\n`go test` / `pytest` / `npm test`","x":1200,"y":90,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"7c8d9e0f1a2b3c4d","type":"text","text":"### Stage 3: Build\n\n构建 Docker 镜像\n\n`registry.example.com/group/svc:${CI_COMMIT_SHA}`","x":1200,"y":180,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d","type":"text","text":"### Stage 4: Scan\n\n安全扫描 (SAST/SCA/容器扫描)\n\n`trivy` / `grype` / `semgrep`","x":1200,"y":270,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d","type":"text","text":"### Stage 5: Push Registry\n\n推送镜像到 GitLab Container Registry\n\n同时打语义化 tag: `v1.2.3`","x":1200,"y":360,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e","type":"text","text":"### Stage 6: Update GitOps\n\n自动修改 `env-config` 仓库的镜像 tag\n\n创建 MR → dev 环境自动合并","x":1200,"y":450,"width":400,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"5d6e7f8a9b0c1d2e","type":"text","text":"### overlays/prod/\n\n生产环境覆盖配置\n\n- 镜像 tag: `v1.2.3` (验收通过版本)\n- 副本数: 3+\n- **严格 MR 审批** (Tech Lead + 运维)","x":1750,"y":470,"width":450,"height":130,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"2a3b4c5d6e7f8a9b","type":"text","text":"**svc-user**\n用户服务","x":0,"y":0,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b","type":"text","text":"**svc-inventory**\n库存服务","x":0,"y":80,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"3f4a5b6c7d8e9f0a","type":"text","text":"### Metrics (指标)\n\n**Prometheus** + **Grafana**\n\n- 服务 QPS / 延迟 / 错误率\n- 资源使用 (CPU/内存)\n- 业务指标\n\n告警规则:\n- P99 延迟 > 500ms\n- 错误率 > 1%\n- Pod 重启","x":0,"y":1150,"width":420,"height":250,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4f5a6b7c8d9e0f1a","type":"text","text":"### Logs (日志)\n\n**CloudWatch** / **ELK** / **Loki**\n\n- 统一日志格式 (JSON)\n- 结构化字段\n- 日志聚合分析\n\n查询:\n- 按 trace_id 关联\n- 按 service 过滤\n- 错误日志告警","x":470,"y":1150,"width":420,"height":250,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a","type":"text","text":"### Traces (调用链)\n\n**Jaeger** / **X-Ray** / **Tempo**\n\n- 分布式追踪\n- 服务调用拓扑\n- 性能瓶颈定位\n\nOpenTelemetry 统一接入:\n- 自动注入 trace context\n- 跨服务链路追踪","x":940,"y":1150,"width":420,"height":250,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"a01b2c3d4e5f6a7b","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2025/cicd 流水线整体 以及版本发布规范.md","x":0,"y":1500,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"b12c3d4e5f6a7b8c","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2025/基于gitlab，进行cicd建设的方案.md","x":450,"y":1500,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"c23d4e5f6a7b8c9d","type":"file","file":"Spaces/4-Archive/ingtube/交接/Inbox/ArgoCD.md","x":900,"y":1500,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"7f8a9b0c1d2e3f4a","type":"text","text":"### 密钥管理\n\n**Vault** / **SealedSecret**\n\n- 敏感信息加密存储\n- 运行时注入\n- 自动轮换\n\nGitLab CI Variables:\n- Masked Variables\n- Protected Variables","x":1450,"y":1150,"width":400,"height":250,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"8f9a0b1c2d3e4f5a","type":"text","text":"### 准入控制\n\n**分支保护**:\n- main/release/* 保护\n- 必须 MR + 至少 1 人 review\n- CI 通过才能合并\n\n**准入标准**:\n- 无单测/CI失败 → 禁止合并\n- 生产 MR 需多人审批","x":1900,"y":1150,"width":400,"height":250,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9f0a1b2c3d4e5f6a","type":"text","text":"### 统一规范\n\n- 代码结构统一\n- CI 模板复用\n- 禁止 kubectl apply\n- 配置收敛到 ConfigMap\n\n**《DevOps 开发指南》**\n- 分支命名规范\n- MR 规范\n- 提测/上线流程","x":2350,"y":1150,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"d34e5f6a7b8c9d0e","type":"file","file":"Calendar/Daily notes/2026/公司 117集群的 kargo.md","x":1350,"y":1500,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"e45f6a7b8c9d0e1f","type":"file","file":"Cards/gitops.md","x":1800,"y":1500,"width":400,"height":100},
		{"id":"2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c","type":"text","text":"**svc-analytics**\n分析服务","x":0,"y":160,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"6b7c8d9e0f1a2b3c","type":"text","text":"**svc-registry**\n服务注册","x":880,"y":160,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d","type":"text","text":"### 分支策略 (Trunk-Based)\n\n`main` (保护) ← `feature/*` / `hotfix/*` → `release/*` (可选)\n\n每个仓库包含: `.gitlab-ci.yml` + `Dockerfile` + 业务代码","x":200,"y":340,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d","type":"text","text":"### CI 模板仓库\n\n`ci-templates/` 统一模板，所有微服务 include 复用\n\n新服务只需复制最小配置即可接入流水线","x":200,"y":440,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c","type":"text","text":"**svc-crawler**\n爬虫服务","x":0,"y":240,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c","type":"text","text":"**svc-llm**\nLLM服务","x":220,"y":240,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"9b0c1d2e3f4a5b6c","type":"text","text":"**svc-embedding**\n向量服务","x":440,"y":240,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"0c1d2e3f4a5b6c7d","type":"text","text":"**svc-scheduler**\n调度服务","x":660,"y":240,"width":200,"height":60},
		{"id":"1c2d3e4f5a6b7c8d","type":"text","text":"**svc-admin**\n管理后台","x":880,"y":240,"width":200,"height":60}
	],
